# Introduction

# 1. AI, ML aur DL: Inka aapsi rishta kya hai?

Aksar log in teen terms mein confuse ho jate hain. Isse aise samjho:
Artificial Intelligence (AI): Ye sabse bada umbrella hai. Iska goal hai machine ko "akalmand" banana taaki wo insaano ki tarah decision le sake.
Machine Learning (ML): Ye AI ka wo raasta hai jahan hum computer ko code nahi karte, balki Data dete hain taaki wo khud patterns pehchan sake.
Deep Learning (DL): Ye ML ka bhi advanced version hai jo hamare brain ke neurons ki tarah kaam karta hai. Ye tab kaam aata hai jab data bahut complex ho (jaise images ya voice).

# 2. Cyber Security mein iska kya kaam?

Pehle ke time mein hum "Signature-based" detection use karte thay—yaani agar virus ka naam 'X' hai, toh use block kar do. Par aaj kal ke attackers har second apna tarika badalte hain.
Anomaly Detection: AI hamare network ka normal behaviour seekh leta hai. Agar koi user achanak se raat ko 3 baje login karke saara data download karne lage, toh AI turant alert bhej dega kyunki ye "abnormal" hai.
Speed: Insaan ko ek log file check karne mein ghanto lagenge, AI ise milliseconds mein kar deta hai.

3. Neural Networks: Machine ka "Chhota Dimaag"

Neural networks hamare biology ke neurons se inspired hain. Inmein teen layers hoti hain:
Input Layer: Jahan data enter hota hai (e.g., ek file ya email).
Hidden Layers: Yahan asli "detective" kaam hota hai. Har layer features check karti hai (e.g., kya is email mein phishing links hain? Kya iska sender unknown hai?).
Output Layer: Final result (e.g., "Safe" ya "Malicious").

# 4. Attackers AI ka kaise use kar rahe hain? (The Dark Side)

Ye sabse important part hai. Agar hum AI use kar rahe hain, toh hackers bhi piche nahi hain:
Smart Phishing: AI aise emails likh sakta hai jo bilkul asli lagein aur jinhe spam filters na pakad sakein.
Deepfakes: Voice aur Video AI ka use karke hackers CEO ban kar employees ko paise transfer karne ka order de sakte hain.
Polymorphic Malware: Aisa virus jo apna dimaag use karke baar-baar apna code badal leta hai taaki antivirus use pehchan na sake.

# 5. Aapka Role kaise badlega?

Darna nahi hai! AI aapki job chheenega nahi, balki aapko "Superpowers" dega.
Aapko manual monitoring (boring kaam) kam karni padegi.
Aapka focus Strategy aur Threat Hunting par zyada hoga.
Aapko ye sikhna hoga ki "AI ko kaise manage karein" aur "AI models ko attacks se kaise bachayein."
